  "important_notes": [
    "All classes are in the DDTrace namespace and defined as C-extension stubs (ext/ddtrace.stub.php).",
    "SpanData.$id and SpanData.$parent and SpanData.$stack are readonly — set by the C runtime.",
    "RootSpanData represents the first span in a trace; carries trace-level metadata (traceId, samplingPriority, origin, gitMetadata).",
    "InferredSpanData is a marker class (no extra fields) used to tag synthetic/inferred spans — referenced by RootSpanData.$inferredSpan.",
    "SpanStack enables async/concurrent context: stacks are linked lists; create_stack() forks, switch_stack() swaps active span.",
    "GitMetadata (commitSha, repositoryUrl) is only attached to RootSpanData, not to child spans.",
    "SpanData.$onClose handlers are cleared on drop; they do NOT fire on drop, only on normal close.",
    "Sampling priority constants: DD_TRACE_PRIORITY_SAMPLING_UNKNOWN is the default on RootSpanData.",
    "meta_struct values are double-msgpack-encoded binary when sent to the agent.",
    "SpanData.$baggage follows OTel baggage semantics — propagated alongside context regardless of trace IDs."
  ]
